scene.message:
Maki: That scientist says he{nl}
knows my mother...{waitkey}{clearbox}But I really don't have any{nl}
mother at all, you hear me!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Those people...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
what kind of research are{nl}
they doing?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: What a shady room.{wait_fr:32}{nl}
I see — so the rumors about{nl}
SEBEC weren't just lies!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Whatever research they{nl}
were doing, it surely wasn't{nl}
something they could do out{nl}
in the open.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: What a dreary room!{nl}
Isn't there anything useful{nl}
lying around?{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: Isn't this the{nl}
basement?{waitkey}Why is this room above{nl}
ground?!{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: On your way here,{nl}
did you meet a woman?{wait_fr:21}{nl}
Short hair, wearing glasses...{waitkey}{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Ah, Sonomura, please, be{nl}
safe!{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: Good heavens! To{nl}
think it would alter the very{nl}
structure of the building...{nl}
this was unforeseen!{waitkey}{ret}
